<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.7.4">
<l>ētalar nakaiceya viḷaiyava raḷaiveṇey</l>
<l>pōtucey tamariya puṉitarnal viraimalar</l>
<l>kōtiya matukaram kulaviya malarmakaḷ</l>
<l>kātalcey kaṇapura maṭikaḷta miṭamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of god, the pure one who was satisfied having eaten</l>
<l>The churned butter of the young girls so that the gossips made fun [of him],</l>
<l>Is Kaṇṇapuram where the lady on a flower, where amble bees</l>
<l>Which burrow in the fine fragrant blossoms, makes love [to him].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
